"""Guardian Aspect CLI module.

Declares AXL extension dependencies. Today the durable surface uses only the
built-in @aspect extension; this file exists so `aspect axl add` can extend
the graph in the future without restructuring the workspace.

The bazel binary version is pinned in .bazeliskrc (shared by bazelisk, the
Aspect CLI, and `guardian run bazel`). This file is NOT the version-of-record
for any binary.
"""
